The paper proposes a method to improve the interpretability of deep neural networks by using logical rules. This topic is closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV) as potential applications of their proposed method. Therefore, these five categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
